<p>You're working the night shift at an old gas station on a rainy night.</p>\

<p>You constantly question why you still work here, but it's the only place that took you in. I mean you had no experience after all, but the more shifts you work the more you realize how horrible and unsafe this job was.</p>\

<p>When you applied, you were desperate, as you were at risk of getting evicted. In order to increase your chances of getting hired, you stated on your application that you could work at any time during any day of the week.</p>\

<p>As a result, your manager took that and ran with it, now it's your 5th day in a row working the [[night shift]].</p>

