<p>You have no choice but to continue working until your coworker takes over for you, but you only have about 10 minutes that you can spare before the bus you take home leaves. After that bus, there's not another one for hours.</p>\

<p>You've been working 5 minutes over and still don't see any sign of your coworker, you begin to get nervous as the minutes go by.</p>\

<p>When you're 7 minutes over and still see no sign of your coworker, you try and phone your manager only to no avail. You find yourself stuck, [[unable to move]].</p>\

