<p>As you wait the rain begins to die down. At least something good is coming out of this.</p>\

<p>Suddenly, a vehicle drives into the gas station and you leap up hoping it's finally your coworker, only for them to pull up to a pump. A family hops out of the SUV and while the mother pumps the gas, the rest of the family head inside.</p>\

<p>As you're trying to take care of this family, you can't help but think of the possible options if you miss your bus. As the SUV pulls off you look at the clock and realize that you've been working 12 minutes over, your [[heart drops]].</p>\

