<p>Finally, after 20 minutes your coworker pulls into the carpark and runs inside. You're about to chew them out but they quickly begin apologizing profusely for being so late.</p>\

<p>They explain that a close relative was hosiptalized and that his family was going through some tough troubles. You apologize for his family troubles and head to the break room to grab your phone and charger only to realize that it wasnt charging again.</p>\

<p>As your phone sits at a measly 15%, you try and contact your closest friends and relatives hoping that someone will answer. Understandibly, none of them answer due to it being at dead of night.</p>\

<p>You can't walk home, as you live miles away from your job. Desperate, you decide to [[hitchhike]].</p>\